## H. Integration Map (Simplified)

| Vendor | Triggered By | Protocol |
|---|---|---|
| **LexisNexis RDP** | VerifyPhone (OTP), CheckDevice, AssessDevicePlusEmailRisk | HTTPS REST |
| **Equifax IDFS** | VerifyPhone, ConfirmPasscode, RequestPasscode | HTTPS SOAP |
| **Equifax DIT** | VerifyPhone (device assessment) | HTTPS REST + OAuth2 |
| **Equifax SMFA** | VerifyPhone, ValidateLink, ResendLink | HTTPS REST + OAuth2 |
| **Experian CrossCore** | VerifyPhone, ConfirmPasscode (Experian path) | HTTPS REST + JWT |
| **CustReg / EntReg** | ConfirmPasscode (final assertion) | HTTPS SOAP |
| **ThreatMetrix** | AssessDevicePlusEmailRisk, CheckDevice | Browser profiling + LexisNexis RDP |
| **Oracle DB** | All endpoints | JDBC via JNDI `ipsWebDS` |

