## L. Recommended Onboarding Order (Quick Reference)

| Order | File | Time | Why |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `ips.properties` | 5m | All URLs, credentials, env config |
| 2 | `RemoteRestResource.java` | 5m | All 26 endpoints in one file |
| 3 | `RemoteRequest.java` + `RemoteResponse.java` | 10m | Input/output contracts |
| 4 | `RemoteProofingValidation.java` | 10m | What gets rejected before biz logic |
| 5 | `RemoteProofingServiceImpl.verifyPhone()` | 20m | Most complex, most-called |
| 6 | `RemoteSupportServiceImpl.checkPhoneVerified()` | 15m | Cross-server state problem |
| 7 | `RemoteProofingServiceImpl.confirmPasscode()` | 15m | Success path endpoint |
| 8 | `RemoteSupportServiceImpl.buildRemoteResponse()` | 10m | Response builder |
| 9 | `RemoteUtilityServiceImpl` | 10m | Config & credential management |

**Total:** ~1.5 hours for solid understanding
